high_descs: Turn right and move to the stove.
Pick up the fork that is on the counter.
Turn right and move to the sink.
Place the fork in the sink.
Turn around and walk toward the counter.
Pick up the fork on the far side of the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two forks to the sink.

high_descs: Go straight, then turn right to go toward the stove.
Pick up the fork from the counter, to the left of the pot.
Go to the sink, to your right.
Put the fork inside of the sink.
Turn around and go to the counter behind you.
Pick up the fork on the counter, to the right of the spoon.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two forks in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter to the immediate left of the stove.
Pick up the fork from between the two knives.
Turn right and move to the sink.
Put the fork in the sink.
Turn and go to the counter directly behind you.
Pick up the fork that is to the left of the square bowl.
Turn around and go back to the sink.
Put the fork into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two forks into the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, then walk towards the stove.
Pick up the fork behind the salt shaker in between two knives.
Turn right, then walk towards the sink.
Place the fork into the sink in front of the potato.
Turn around, then walk towards the counter top.
Pick up the fork located in between a square bowl and a gold spoon.
Turn around and walk towards the sink.
Place the fork on the left side in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two forks into a sink.
